        "description": "The turbulence closure and hemolysis sub-model must be justified against published literature for rotating blood-contacting devices; sensitivity of hemolysis predictions to turbulence model choice must be quantified. Achieved: SST k-ω selected based on published benchmark studies; turbulence model sensitivity study shows ±9% variation in hemolysis index — documented and included in Monte Carlo ensemble."
